com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class DefaultManageWorkforceTimesheetService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultManageWorkforceTimesheetService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManageWorkforceTimesheetService

    @Named
public class DefaultManageWorkforceTimesheetService
extends Object
implements ManageWorkforceTimesheetService

    This service enables you to create, read, update and delete (CRUD) data related to Timesheet of a workforce (Employees or Contingent Workers) with the data provided in a payload, in an API call. This service also supports automatic posting of Timesheet data to Controlling synchronously.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_MANAGE_WORKFORCE_TIMESHEET
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Workforce Timesheet Integration (SAP_COM_0027), Workforce Timesheet Integration (SAP_COM_0027)
    Scope Items:Time Recording (1Q4), Time Recording - Project-Based Services (J12)
